dictionary.title: Data Dictionary
dictionary.main.paragraph: The CQDG Data Dictionary provides information about the structure and content of the database. It defines the specific formats and restrictions for each data field. Data from studies participating in the CQDG must be entirely compatible with the latest version of the CQDG Data Dictionary to ensure a standard of data quality.
